A CONCERT is being held on Sunday night in Cottiers Theatre in the West End to raise funds for cancer research.Money raised by the elector-flute concerts given by Kim Hickey, who is travelling from American to stage will go to Beat Blood Cancer/Leukaemia and Lymphoma Research and for World Child Cancer.For more information on the &quot;Old, New, Borrowed and Blue&quot; concert go to http://www.cottiers.com/events/old-new-borrowed-blue/